  <bioghist id="aspace_0b7f655cc8973e2de14115209f0891fa">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Vietnam War veteran.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_7a8bf15fb05b01ff90211589de8a39ed">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes letters to family, certificates and medals, maps, Army records, insignia, receipts, and memorabilia of a helicopter pilot in the Vietnam War. Also, videocassette of movies taken in Vietnam and tape recordings sent home during the war; includes family papers and business records, and photographs.</p>  </scopecontent>
